  				<div class="col-md-8"><h3 class="green">School & Pedestrian crossings</h3>
  					<p class="beta-p left">If you are within 20 metres of a pedestrian crossing, footbridge, underpass or traffic signals, you must use it to cross the road.</p>
						<p class="beta-p left">Don't dawdle on a pedestrian crossing.</p>
						<p class="beta-p left">Don't step out suddenly onto a pedestrian crossing if any vehicles are so close to the crossing that they cannot stop.</p>
  				</div>
