   						<p class="beta-p left"></p>
   						<p class="beta-p left">Here's another tip, remember, it takes time for a vehicle to stop. Be sensible and wait for a gap in the traffic before crossing the road.</p>
   						<p class="beta-p left">If you can get a copie of the new Zealand road code and read it ! you will be a better pedestrian and become more confident when you know the road rules.</p>
